title: Once Upon A Time... The Defenders - Redux!
description:
The 1969-1972 comics that lead up to The Defenders.  This zip archive includes:

Dr Strange 183
Sub-Mariner 22
Incredible Hulk 126
Marvel Feature 1-3 
The Defenders 1-11 (the first story arc)

Not always deliberately connected, but this was the broken series of stories that spawned The Defenders in 1971.
